    #benefits
      
      .row.benefits-article
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4
          = image_tag "easy-as-abc-blocks.png", :class => "img-center img-responsive", :title => "Image of classic style broadcast microphone"
        
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-8
        %h2 Tell Your Story Easily
        %p Your unique story and voice is valuable to bloggers and journalists desperately seeking relevant content and stories to share with their readership.</p>
        %p We make it simple to curate your promotional materials into an congruent story. Made as simple as social networking platforms. Upload, organize, highlight, and tell your story to the people who want to share with a simple url link.
    
      .div-border-thin-blue-ratio
    
      .row.benefits-article
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-8
          %h2 Modern and Responsive
          %p Old-style websites are just not effective on phones and tablets, too much clicking and page loading.
          %p Your Entreuse EPK Storyboard is built for today's mobile users so you look good no matter what size screen.
        
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4
          = image_tag "responsive-design.png", :class => "img-center img-responsive", :title => "Image of Entreuse Home Page displayed on different devices"
    
      .div-border-thin-blue-ratio
    
      .row.benefits-article
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4
          = image_tag "press-hat.png", :class => "img-center img-responsive", :title => "Image of Fadora hat with Press Label"
          
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-8
          %h2 Designed for Professionals
          %p Our favorite newspaper editor complains about getting press releases that are not relevant to her readers, no pictures, lack of important details, and overall, "Where is the story I care about?".
          %p Make editors everywhere happy with the materials they need to help get your story told. Your story matters, present it properly so it gets told more often.

  #about.panel
    %h2.text-center The Team
    .row
      .col-xs-10.col-sm-4.col-md-3.col-lg-3
        = image_tag "f1-sandy-l-fishler.png", :title => "Sandy L. Fischler, Entreuse Founder", :class => "img-center img-responsive image-md img-margin img-styling-basic"
        
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-9.founder
        %p
          %span.name-hilite Sandy Fischler
        %p Sandy is a marketing and special events freelance professional who wants a better way to promote, not only her clients' work, her work as well. Together with her businss partner, they have built Entreuse for themselves and for everyone else who needs a to get attention for what they do. 
        %p Sandy is a graduate of The Founder Institute, where Entreuse was incubated/accelerated under the guidance of highly experienced entrepreneur mentors. 
        
    .row
      .col-xs-10.col-sm-4.col-md-3
        = image_tag "f1-jayson-t-perry.png", :title => "Jayson T. Perry, Entreuse Founder", :class => "img-center img-responsive image-md img-margin img-styling-basic"  
        
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-9.founder
        %p
          %span.name-hilite Jayson Perry 
        %p Jayson is a 20-year music industry gaining expertise in a record label that insisted their A&amp;R executives also be experience marketing and promotions professionals. This is where he learned the value of a good "story" presented in a  dynomite package.
        %p With his partner, Sandy, Jayson set-out to create the App that helps him, and others, present the story in way that is compelling and geared to create momentum.
  
